    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at this risk level. Uncertainty quantification demonstrated that the 95th-percentile RH index remains below the acceptance criterion of 1.0 across the full UQ ensemble. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
